<div class="small-12 large-9 columns messages">
	<h1>
		{{#sentMessages}}Sent messages{{/sentMessages}}
		{{^sentMessages}}Inbox{{/sentMessages}}
		{{^loading}}
			{{#message-count}} ({{message-count}}){{/message-count}}
		{{/loading}}
	</h1>
	<span class="message-count">
		{{^loading}}
			{{#message-count}}
				Showing {{first-on-page}}-{{last-on-page}} of {{message-count}} messages
			{{/message-count}}
			{{^message-count}}
				0 messages
			{{/message-count}}
		{{/loading}}
	</span>
    {{^sentMessages}}<p class="small-text guidelines">Lender messages should always abide by <a href="{{guidelines-url}}">Kiva's community guidelines</a>.</p>{{/sentMessages}}
	<div class="message-list-wrapper {{#message-count}}has-messages{{/message-count}} {{#loading}}loading{{/loading}}">
		<div class="loader-overlay">
			{{> 01-molecules/03-media/01-loading-spinner }}
		</div>
		<ul class="message-list">
			{{#messages}}
				<li>
					{{> 02-organisms/21-messages/01-lender-message }}
				</li>
			{{/messages}}
		</ul>
	</div>
	{{^loading}}
		{{^message-count}}
			{{#sentMessages}}
				<p>You haven't sent any lender messages.</p>
				<p>You can send a message directly from another lender's public profile, or by replying to a message you've received. You must have a public lender profile to use lender messages.</p>
			{{/sentMessages}}
			{{^sentMessages}}
				<p>Lender messages allow you to communicate directly with other lenders through the Kiva website, building stronger community with one another. You can send a message directly from another lender's public profile, or by replying to a message you've received.</p>
				<p>You must have a public lender profile to use lender messages.</p>
			{{/sentMessages}}
		{{/message-count}}
	{{/loading}}
	<div class="pagination-region">
		{{> 01-molecules/05-navigation/07-pagination }}
	</div>
</div>
<div class="spacer" style="clear:both"></div>